## Evidence Provenance

Every finding in this report is backed by evidence atoms produced by specific
tool executions. The full audit trail is available in the JSONL log files under
the `analysis/audit/` directory.

- `execution_log.jsonl` — Every tool command executed
- `findings_log.jsonl` — Every finding registered and updated
- `contradiction_log.jsonl` — Every contradiction detected
- `correction_log.jsonl` — Every self-correction iteration

**EvidenceChain** — Autonomous forensic investigation with architectural self-correction.
